## **Authentication Routes**

| Method | Endpoint        | Description         | Body / Headers |
|--------|----------------|-------------------|----------------|
| POST   | /users/register | Register new user  | `{ username, email, password }` |
| POST   | /users/login    | Login user         | `{ email, password }` |
| GET    | /users/profile  | Get logged-in user | Header: `Authorization: Bearer <JWT>` |

---

## **Product Routes**

### Public

| Method | Endpoint               | Description                  |
|--------|-----------------------|-----------------------------|
| GET    | /products             | Get all products            |
| GET    | /products/featured    | Get featured products       |
| GET    | /products/:id         | Get single product by ID    |

### Admin

| Method | Endpoint            | Description                 | Body / Headers |
|--------|-------------------|----------------------------|----------------|
| POST   | /products/create   | Create new product          | `{ name, category, price, stock, ... }` + Admin JWT |
| PUT    | /products/:id      | Update product             | `{ fields to update }` + Admin JWT |
| DELETE | /products/:id      | Delete product             | Admin JWT |

---

## **Cart Routes**  

All cart routes require a valid **user JWT**.

| Method | Endpoint           | Description                 | Body |
|--------|------------------|-----------------------------|------|
| GET    | /cart             | Get logged-in userâ€™s cart   | - |
| POST   | /cart/add         | Add product to cart         | `{ productId, qty }` |
| DELETE | /cart/remove/:itemId | Remove item from cart     | - |
| DELETE | /cart/clear       | Clear entire cart           | - |

