## **Order Routes**

### User

| Method | Endpoint          | Description                 | Body / Headers |
|--------|-----------------|----------------------------|----------------|
| POST   | /orders/create   | Create order from cart      | User JWT |
| GET    | /orders/my-orders | Get logged-in user orders  | User JWT |

### Admin

| Method | Endpoint           | Description                | Body / Headers |
|--------|------------------|---------------------------|----------------|
| GET    | /orders/all       | Get all orders            | Admin JWT |
| PUT    | /orders/:id/status | Update order status       | `{ status: "pending"|"paid"|"shipped"|"delivered" }` + Admin JWT |

---

## Notes
- Use **Bearer token** in `Authorization` header for all protected routes.
- `status` for orders can be: `"pending"`, `"paid"`, `"shipped"`, `"delivered"`.
- All IDs are **MongoDB ObjectIds**.

